name: Evolved Bunny Berserker
description: This year's Bunny Berserker armor is as fierce as it is fuzzy! Find the Magical Marshmallow Cheep, The Gold-Foil Chocolate Bunny, and the Basketful of Dyed Eggs dropping off of the bosses in Greenguard forest and use them in Cabdury's merge shop. Happy Grenwog!
